Package: BLASTr
Title: Parallel Taxonomic Classification of Metabarcoding Sequences
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lucio", "Queiroz", , "luciorqueiroz@gmail.com", role = "aut",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6090-1834")),
    person("Heron", "Hilario", , "heronoh@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2548-1053"))
  )
Description: Seamlessly run BLAST searches within R, tailored for ASV
    (Amplicon Sequence Variant) analysis.  This package offers a robust
    set of functions designed to efficiently identify and process
    sequences from high-throughput metagenomicmetagenomic experiments,
    following best practices for sequence data analysis.
